      "role": "user",
      "content": "Okay, i get the strategy, but I need the actual talking points. Give me a specific response I can coach the candidate to use when the reporter asks, \"Why are you supporting a bill you said was a disaster only three weeks ago?\" We need it to sound convincing so they don't see through the pivot.",
